quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Iqtaraba linnasi hisabuhumwahum fee ghaflatin muAAridoon"
  21,2,"Ma ya/teehim min thikrin minrabbihim muhdathin illa istamaAAoohu wahumyalAAaboon"
  21,3,"Lahiyatan quloobuhum waasarroo annajwaallatheena thalamoo hal hatha illabasharun mithlukum afata/toona assihra waantum tubsiroon"
  21,4,"Qala rabbee yaAAlamu alqawla fee assama-iwal-ardi wahuwa assameeAAu alAAaleem"
  21,5,"Bal qaloo adghathu ahlaminbali iftarahu bal huwa shaAAirun falya/tinabi-ayatin kama orsila al-awwaloon"
  21,6,"Ma amanat qablahum min qaryatinahlaknaha afahum yu/minoon"
  21,7,"Wama arsalna qablaka illarijalan noohee ilayhim fas-aloo ahla aththikriin kuntum la taAAlamoon"
  21,8,"Wama jaAAalnahum jasadan laya/kuloona attaAAama wama kanookhalideen"
  21,9,"Thumma sadaqnahumu alwaAAdafaanjaynahum waman nashao waahlaknaalmusrifeen"
  21,10,"Laqad anzalna ilaykum kitabanfeehi thikrukum afala taAAqiloon"